# Feature: herald curtain inspect — populated stage board (atlas/beacon/lumen).
Output ../assets/demo-inspect.gif
Output build/demo-inspect.txt
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Hide
Type "export PS1='demo$ '; export PATH=\"$HOME/bin:$PATH\"; unset TMUX; clear"
Enter
Show
Type "herald curtain inspect"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
